reports.description:
Birthdays report

Find all records with policy holder birth date coming in next 2 months
Include birthdays starting from today, max 20 records in the report

SQL query (please note, sql query may include coldfusion code for better understanding ): 
DECLARE @StartDate datetime, @EndDate datetime
            SET @StartDate = DATEADD(dd, -1, getDate())
            SET @EndDate   = DATEADD(mm, 2, @StartDate)

            SELECT TOP 20
               R.CONTRACTNUMBER,
               R.POLICYHOLDERNAME,
               R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH,
               PD.PHONEPRIVATE as telephone,
               PD.PHONEMOBILE  as mobile,
               PD.EMAIL as email,
               DATEPART(month, CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105)) AS Month,
               DATEPART(day, CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105)) AS Day
             FROM P_RECORD R
             JOIN P_CONTRACTDATA PC ON PC.ID = R.CONTRACTDATA_ID
             JOIN P_CLIENTDATA   PCL ON PCL.ID = PC.CLIENTDATA_ID
             JOIN P_POLICYHOLDER PP  ON PP.ID = PCL.POLICYHOLDER_ID
             JOIN P_PERSONALDATA PD  ON PD.ID = PP.PERSONALDATA_ID
            WHERE
                   R.IFILEPROCESSED_ID IS NULL
              AND  (
                    DATEADD(year, DATEDIFF(year,  CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105), @StartDate), CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105)) BETWEEN @StartDate AND @EndDate
                    OR DATEADD(year, DATEDIFF(year,  CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105), @EndDate), CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105)) BETWEEN @StartDate AND @EndDate
                   )
              AND
                (
                   #preserveSingleQuotes(variables.distributorPermissionSqlConditionIFile)#
                )
                ORDER BY
                CASE WHEN DATEADD(YEAR, DATEDIFF(YEAR,  CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105), @StartDate), CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105)) BETWEEN @StartDate AND @EndDate THEN 1 ELSE 2 END,
                          DATEPART(month, CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105)), DATEPART(day, CONVERT(datetime, R.POLICYHOLDERDATEOFBIRTH, 105))

reports.description:
Unpaid premium

Fetch all contracts that are
- ACTIVE and not paid up
- have an overdue payment that we can match with planned payment (there exists overdue payments that are not planned but are not displayed) i.e. overdue 01.02 and 01.03 but planned is only 01.02
- we filter based on user right to see other agents contracts, if user is an agent and can see only his owns then we check sales agent code for overdue payment records
- we take all follow ups created after overdue payment was detected



SQL query (please note, sql query may include coldfusion code for better understanding ): 
  SELECT
             R.DISTRIBUTORID            AS masterDistributorId,
             R.VERMITTLERNUMMER         AS salesAgentCode,
             T.AGENTLASTNAME + ' ' +    T.AGENTFIRSTNAME           AS agentName,
             R.CONTRACTNUMBER           AS contractNumber,
             R.APPLICATIONNUMBER        AS applicationNumber,
             R.POLICYHOLDERNAME         AS policyHolderName,
             R.CONTRACTSTARTDATE        AS contractStartDate,
             STAT.EXISTSREMINDER        AS hasReminder,
             STAT.EXISTSFOLLOWUP        AS hasFollowUp,
             PO.DUEDATE                 AS overdueDueDate,
             PO.CURRENCY                AS currency,
             CASE R.SUBSTATUS WHEN 'ACTNFP' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS isFirstPremium,                -- sub status indicate that this is missing first payment
             PO.DEBIT                   AS debit,
             PO.PAYMENTFREQUENCY        AS overduePaymentFrequency,
             F.FOLLOWUPCREATED          AS followUpCreateDate,
             F.FOLLOWUPDATEFINISHED     AS followUpFinishedDate,
             F.FOLLOWUPTEXT             AS followUpText,
             F.FOLLOWUPTYPE             AS followUpType,
             T.PREMIUM                  AS premium,
             1 AS showThisRecord
             FROM P_RECORD R
             JOIN P_CONTRACTDATA C ON R.CONTRACTDATA_ID = C.ID
			 JOIN P_TECHNICALDATA T ON C.CURRENTTECHNICALDATA_ID = T.ID
             JOIN P_STATUSDATA STAT ON R.STATUSDATA_ID = STAT.ID
             JOIN P_STATUSDATA_P_OVERDUEPAYMENT PSO ON R.STATUSDATA_ID = PSO.P_STATUSDATA_ID
             JOIN P_OVERDUEPAYMENT PO ON PO.ID = PSO.OVERDUEPAYMENTS_ID
             LEFT JOIN P_STATUSDATA_P_FOLLOWUP SF ON STAT.ID = SF.P_STATUSDATA_ID
             LEFT JOIN P_FOLLOWUP F ON SF.FOLLOWUPS_ID = F.ID
             WHERE
             R.IFILEPROCESSED_ID IS NULL
             AND R.STATUS='ACTIVE'
             AND R.SUBSTATUS != 'ACTMPU'
             AND STAT.EXISTSOVERDUEPAYMENT = 1  -- if this flag is set then there exists entries in P_OVERDUEPAYMENT table

             <cfif application.mfilos.marketConfiguration.isFranceMarket() or application.mfilos.marketConfiguration.isBelgiumMarket()>
                AND F.FOLLOWUPTYPE IN ('RIDREFUS','CHEQNCOV','RIDSECAT', 'REMPAYFO', 'SEPAMANDREF', 'MAVUNPAID', 'REMINDER', 'RIBINCOM', 'RIBREFUS', 'RIBREQST', 'FTPRNTPD', 'DEBTRETN')
             <cfelse>
                AND F.FOLLOWUPTYPE IN ('RIDREFUS','CHEQNCOV','RIDSECAT', 'REMPAYFO', 'SEPAMANDREF', 'MAVUNPAID', 'REMINDER')
             </cfif>
             AND
                (
                   #preserveSingleQuotes(variables.distributorPermissionSqlConditionIFile)#
                )
             ORDER BY PO.DUEDATE ASC

SQL Production Report query (please note, sql query may include coldfusion code for better understanding ): 
DECLARE @min_creation_date_application DATETIME = getdate() - #application.mfilos.systemConfigurationValues.getVisibleTimeApplication()#;

            SELECT
            PA.APPLICATION_NR,
            PI.ILLUSTRATION_NR,
            PA.DISTRIBUTOR_ID,
            DC.DISTRIBUTOR_FULL_NAME,
            PVSM.VISIBLE_STATUS,
            PSM_SIGNED.DATE AS APPLICATION_SIGNATURE_DATE,
            PSM_APPROVED.DATE AS APPLICATION_APPROVAL_DATE,
            PSM_EXTENDED.DATE AS APPLICATION_EXTENDED_DATE,
            PTDAM.START_DATE,
            PPAM.PAYMENT_METHOD_FIRST_PREMIUM,
            PA.PRODUCT_NAME,
            PA.TARIFF_NAME,
            CASE WHEN PI.SIGN_POS_GUID IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS IS_ILLUSTRATION_SIGNED_DIGITALLY,
            CASE WHEN PA.SIGN_POS_GUID IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS IS_APPLICATION_SIGNED_DIGITALLY,
            PTDAM.POLICY_TERM,
            PTDAM.INSTALMENT_AMOUNT,
            PTDAM.INSTALMENT_PLAN,
            PTDAM.ANNUAL_PREMIUM,
            PTDAM.INITIAL_LUMP_PREMIUM_AMOUNT,
            PTDAM.DYNAMIC_OPTION,
            PA.AGENT_CODE,
            PIAM.FISCAL_CODE,
            PEPAM.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + PEPAM.LAST_NAME_FIRST + ' ' + PEPAM.LAST_NAME_SECOND AS PH_NAME,
            CASE RT.CALCULATED_RISK_TYPE_ID
              WHEN 1 THEN 'A'
              WHEN 2 THEN 'B'
              WHEN 3 THEN 'C'
              WHEN 4 THEN 'D'
              WHEN 5 THEN 'E'
            END AS CALCULATED_RISK_TYPE,
            CASE PA.SELECTED_RISK_TYPE
              WHEN 1 THEN 'A'
              WHEN 2 THEN 'B'
              WHEN 3 THEN 'C'
              WHEN 4 THEN 'D'
              WHEN 5 THEN 'E'
            END AS APPLICATION_RISK_TYPE,
            U.DESCRIPTION AS AGENT_DESCRIPTION,
            U.FIRSTNAME AS AGENT_FIRSTNAME,
            U.LASTNAME AS AGENT_LASTNAME

            FROM POS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PA
            LEFT JOIN POS_ILLUSTRATIONS_MFILOS PI ON PA.ILLUSTRATION_ID = PI.ILLUSTRATION_ID
            LEFT JOIN CPM_RISK_TYPE RT ON PA.FK_RISK_TYPE_ID = RT.RISK_TYPE_ID
            LEFT JOIN DISTRIBUTOR_CONFIGURATION DC ON PA.DISTRIBUTOR_ID = DC.DISTRIBUTOR_ID
            LEFT JOIN POS_VISIBLE_STATUS_MFILOS PVSM ON PA.STATUS = PVSM.DB_STATUS
            LEFT JOIN POS_STATUSCHANGES_MFILOS  PSM_SIGNED ON PA.APPLICATION_ID = PSM_SIGNED.FK_APPLICATION_ID AND PSM_SIGNED.STATUS='signed application'
            LEFT JOIN POS_STATUSCHANGES_MFILOS  PSM_APPROVED ON PA.APPLICATION_ID = PSM_APPROVED.FK_APPLICATION_ID AND PSM_APPROVED.STATUS='approved application'
            LEFT JOIN POS_STATUSCHANGES_MFILOS  PSM_EXTENDED ON PA.APPLICATION_ID = PSM_EXTENDED.FK_APPLICATION_ID AND PSM_EXTENDED.STATUS='extended check'
            LEFT JOIN POS_TECHNICAL_DETAILS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PTDAM ON PA.APPLICATION_ID = PTDAM.FK_APPLICATION_ID
            LEFT JOIN POS_PAYMENTS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PPAM ON PA.APPLICATION_ID = PPAM.FK_APPLICATION_ID
            LEFT JOIN POS_PERSONS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PEPAM ON PA.APPLICATION_ID = PEPAM.FK_APPLICATION_ID AND PEPAM.DISCRIMINATOR='PH'
            LEFT JOIN POS_IDENTIFICATIONS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PIAM ON PEPAM.ID = PIAM.FK_PERSON_ID
            LEFT JOIN #local.fullQualifiedUMGPath#.[USERS] U ON PA.AGENT_CODE = U.SALESAGENTCODE COLLATE SQL_Latin1_General_CP1_CI_AS

            WHERE
            PVSM.LANGUAGE = :language
            AND PA.CREATION_DATE > @min_creation_date_application
            AND PA.STATUS IN ('signed application', 'approved application', 'extended check')
            AND (PSM_SIGNED.DATE IN (SELECT MAX(DATE) FROM POS_STATUSCHANGES_MFILOS WHERE FK_APPLICATION_ID=PA.APPLICATION_ID AND STATUS='signed application') OR PSM_SIGNED.DATE IS NULL)
            AND (PSM_APPROVED.DATE IN (SELECT MAX(DATE) FROM POS_STATUSCHANGES_MFILOS WHERE FK_APPLICATION_ID=PA.APPLICATION_ID AND STATUS='approved application') OR PSM_APPROVED.DATE IS NULL)
            AND (PSM_EXTENDED.DATE = (SELECT MAX(DATE) FROM POS_STATUSCHANGES_MFILOS WHERE FK_APPLICATION_ID=PA.APPLICATION_ID AND STATUS='extended check') OR PSM_EXTENDED.DATE IS NULL)
            #local.distributorPermissionSqlCondition#
            ORDER BY PA.DISTRIBUTOR_ID ASC

issuedPolicyStartDateMin = 1st day of current month
notIssuedPolicyStartDateMin = 1st day of previous month
policyIssuanceDateMin = 45 days before current date


SQL query (please note, sql query may include coldfusion code for better understanding ): 
SELECT * FROM(
            SELECT
            PA.APPLICATION_NR,
            PA.CONTRACT_NR,
            PP.TITLE,
            PP.COMPANY_NAME,
            PP.FIRST_NAME,
            <cfif application.mfilos.marketConfiguration.isSpainMarket()>
                PP.LAST_NAME_FIRST + ' ' + PP.LAST_NAME_SECOND,
            <cfelse>
                PP.LAST_NAME,
            </cfif>
            PT.START_DATE,
            PA.CONTRACT_CONFIRM_DATE,
            PA.AGENT_CODE,
            PA.AGENT_FIRST_NAME,
            PA.AGENT_LAST_NAME,
            PA.DISTRIBUTOR_ID,
            PA.MASTER_DISTRIBUTOR_ID,
            PA.STATUS,
            'EXTENDED_CHECK' = case when (select count(*)
            from POS_BOS_TRANSFER_HISTORY_APPLICATIONS where POS_BOS_TRANSFER_HISTORY_APPLICATIONS.APPLICATION_NR = PA.APPLICATION_NR AND POS_BOS_TRANSFER_HISTORY_APPLICATIONS.IS_TRANSFER_SUCCESSFUL=1
            AND POS_BOS_TRANSFER_HISTORY_APPLICATIONS.TRANSFER_TYPE='APPLICATION_WITHOUT_POLICY') > 0 then 1 else 0 end
            FROM POS_TECHNICAL_DETAILS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PT
            JOIN POS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PA ON PT.FK_APPLICATION_ID= PA.APPLICATION_ID
            JOIN POS_PERSONS_APPLICATIONS_MFILOS PP ON PP.FK_APPLICATION_ID = PA.APPLICATION_ID
            WHERE PA.DISTRIBUTOR_ID =
            <cfqueryparam value="#arguments.distributorId#" cfsqltype="CF_SQL_VARCHAR"/>
            AND (
                (START_DATE >= #arguments.issuedPolicyStartDateMin#)
                OR
                (START_DATE >= #arguments.notIssuedPolicyStartDateMin# AND PA.STATUS = 'extended_check')
            )
            AND (
                (CONTRACT_DATE >= #arguments.policyIssuanceDateMin# OR CONTRACT_DATE IS NULL) --some contracts have no CONTRACT_DATE set in mFilos (i.e.'extended_check_accepted_with_changes')
